text: Mohammad Khaledur Rahman Tito (1 March 1945 - 10 January 2021) was a Bangladesh Awami League politician. He was a member of the Awami League. In 1986, he was elected to the Jatiya Sangsad. He left the job in 1988 and was re-elect to the parliament in 2008. Tito retired in 2014. Tito died on 10 January 2021 in Jessore, Bangladesh at the age of 74. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Politicians from Khulna Division Category:2021 deaths Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:9th Jatiya Sangsad members
